      • stripComments

        public static CharSequence stripComments(CharSequence seq)
        Strip any c-style block comments, e.g slash-star to star-slash. Note: this function down not correctly handle nested comment blocks. Note: this function is a bit greedy, and will incorrectly strip comments inside strings, but this shouldn't be a problem for memory config files.
        Parameters:
        seq - The content of a file that might contain c-style block-comments
        Returns:
        The same content, that has now had all block-comments stripped out.
